      "span_text": "For straightforward applications of paradigmatic factor analytic, structural equation, item response, and latent class models, traditional estimation is fairly routine, accurate, and accessible via widelyavailable software e.g., Mislevy Nevertheless, when researchers want to push the boundaries of even these complex modeling paradigms, they may benefit by turning to MCMC Segawa et al.  ."
